query: SELECT p.id, p.name, p.civilId, COUNT(*) as test_count FROM patients p JOIN virologyTests vt ON p.id = vt.patientId WHERE p.id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT patientId FROM virologyTests WHERE viralLoad IS NOT NULL AND viralLoad != '' AND viralLoad != '0' AND viralLoad != '0.00') GROUP BY p.id HAVING test_count >= 3 ORDER BY test_count DESC LIMIT 5;
